instruction: Come up with a list of things to include in a first aid kit.
output:
1. Gauze pads
2. Bandages
3. Adhesive tape
4. Antiseptic wipes and cream
5. Disposable gloves
6. Tweezers
7. Safety pins
8. Sterile eye wash
9. Pain relievers
10. Burn cream
11. Scissors
12. Instant Cold Compress
13. Oral thermometer
14. Oral rehydration salts
15. Eye drops
16. Insect sting relief pads
17. CPR face shields
18. Splint
19. Sunscreen
